videos.description: Lousiville's Mariya Moore finds the cutting Asia Durr with the great pass for the easy bucket.
videos.headline: Louisville with the great pass for the Durr Layup

videos.description: Notre Dame's Brianna Turner uses the spin to get open and jumps up to tip in the pass from Arike Ogunbowale.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Turner with the nice move to tip in the pass

videos.description: Kathryn Westbeld gets the steal and throws the long pass to Lindsay Allen for the layup for Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Notre Dame gets the steal and throws the long pass for the Allen layup

videos.description: Notre Dame's Brianna Turner blocks the shot and it leads to  Marina Mabrey finishing the layup with the nice Euro- step.
videos.headline: Notre Dame gets the block which leads to the nice layup for Mabrey

videos.description: Notre Dame's Lindsay Allen with the great pass to Jackie Young for the layup.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Allen with the great pass for the layup

videos.description: Notre Dame's Lindsay Allen gets the ball stolen by Taylor Johnson but she hustles all the way back and blocks the layup.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Allen loses the ball but hustles to block the layup attempt by Louisville

videos.description: Notre Dame's Arike Ogunbowale drives and makes the the layup and gets fouled.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Ogunbowale makes the tough layup plus the foul

videos.description: Notre Dame's Arike Ogunbowale steals the pass and goes all the way for the layup.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Ogunbowale gets the steal and goes all the way for the layup

videos.description: Notre Dame head coach Muffet Mcgraw happy with the team played and only having 3 turnovers in the win over Louisville.
videos.headline: Notre Dame head coach Muffet Mcgraw breaking down their 85-66 win over Louisville
